&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For what it&apos;s worth, GSON lets you register an &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/google/gson/blob/master/UserGuide.md#TOC-Writing-an-Instance-Creator&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;instance creator&lt;/a&gt;&#160;that I think would handle this particular case for you as a workaround (or anybody reading this in the future who needs it to work on an older version that is missing the constructor).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
